 Looking ahead, Zikalala said, the aim was to ensure that other cities as well in the province also benefited from the upsurge in wealth.
 "We have a strategy in place to woo investors into to areas such as Richards Bay, Port Sheptstone and Newcastle so that the economies of these towns also improve."

